2Fa%3E%20over%20its%20slow%20AI%20adoption.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20seeing%20a%20receptivity%20in%20this%20region%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20kingdom%2C%26quot%3B%20Karp%20said%20at%20the%20Saudi-US%20Investment%20Forum%20on%20Tuesday.%20%26quot%3BBut%20the%20receptivity%20is%20on%20the%20back%20of%20people%20who%20have%20a%20deep%20tradition%20in%20engineering%20excellence%20and%2C%20quite%20frankly%2C%20believe%20in%20their%20own%20future.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKarp%20was%20addressing%20a%20request%20from%20panel%20host%20and%20CNBC%20anchor%20Sara%20Eisen%20to%20expand%20upon%20a%20previous%20comment%20that%20the%20countries%20and%20regions%20that%20are%20best%20utilizing%20AI%20right%20now%20are%20the%20US%20and%20the%20Middle%20East.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BObviously%2C%20the%20great%20contradistinction%20here%20is%20Europe%2C%20where%2C%20you%20know%2C%20it's%20like%20people%20have%20given%20up%2C%20and%20we%20%E2%80%94%20I%20really%20hope%20that%20turns%20around%20in%20Europe%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20talk%20came%20as%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20received%20a%20royal%20welcome%20with%20golden%20chairs%20and%20Arabian%20horses%20in%20Riyadh%20on%20Tuesday%20as%20he%20kicked%20off%20his%20Gulf%20tour.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-saudi-arabia-investment-conference-business-tech-leaders-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EFlanked%20by%20executives%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20Google%2C%20Nvidia%2C%20BlackRock%2C%20and%20others%20to%20discuss%20AI%2C%20defense%2C%20and%20energy%20with%20Saudi%20officials%2C%20Trump%20said%20he%20aims%20to%20secure%20%241%20trillion%20in%20deals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20an%20October%202024%20report%20published%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mckinsey.com%2Fcapabilities%2Fquantumblack%2Four-insights%2Ftime-to-place-our-bets-europes-ai-opportunity%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EQuantumBlack%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20AI%20by%20McKinsey%2C%20European%20organizations%20lag%20behind%20their%20US%20counterparts%20by%2045%20to%2070%25%20in%20terms%20of%20AI%20adoption.%20And%20while%20Europe%20leads%20in%20producing%20AI%20semiconductor%20equipment%20%E2%80%94%20machinery%20and%20tools%20used%20to%20make%20semiconductors%20%E2%80%94%20the%20report%20said%20that%20Europe%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ehas%20below%205%25%20market%20share%20in%20areas%20like%20raw%20materials%2C%20cloud%20infrastructure%2C%20and%20supercomputers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOpportunity%20remains%20wide%20open%2C%20but%20Europe%20is%20starting%20from%20a%20disadvantage%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20QuantumBlack%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEurope%20is%20also%20known%20for%20much%20more%20stringent%20AI%20regulations.%20On%20August%201%2C%202024%2C%20Europe%20enacted%20the%20AI%20Act%2C%20the%20first-ever%20legal%20framework%20on%20AI%2C%20and%20established%20an%20AI%20office%20to%20oversee%20the%20implementation%20of%20these%20regulations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AI%20Act%20is%20just%20one%20part%20of%20a%20wider%20package%20of%20measures%20that%20the%20EU%20said%20ensures%20%26quot%3Btrustworthy%20AI%2C%26quot%3B%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewhich%20explicitly%20banned%20practices%20such%20as%20AI-based%20manipulation%20and%20deception%2C%20real-time%20remote%20biometric%20identification%20for%20law%20enforcement%20purposes%20in%20public%20spaces%2C%20and%20individual%20criminal%20offense%20risk%20assessment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feuropean-union-trying-regulate-ai-artificial-intelligence-could-backfire-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20Act%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20ways%20of%20using%20AI%2C%20such%20as%20robot-assisted%20surgery%20and%20credit%20scoring%2C%20are%20also%20categorized%20as%20%26quot%3Bhigh-risk%26quot%3B%20and%20subjected%20to%20strict%20scrutiny.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best-known%20European%20AI%20company%20that%20raised%20the%20most%20amount%20of%20fu