The%20freak%20offs%20became%20my%20job%2C%26quot%3B%20Ventura%20testified.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20early%202006%2C%20Ventura%20signed%20a%2010-album%20deal%20with%20Combs'%20label%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdiddy-documentary-peacock-details-takeaways-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBad%20Boy%20Records%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20recorded%20%26quot%3Bhundreds%20of%20songs%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20subsequent%20years%2C%20but%20many%20%26quot%3Bdidn't%20see%20the%20light%20of%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20testified%20on%20the%20witness%20stand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnly%20a%20handful%20of%20Ventura's%20songs%20were%20officially%20released%20following%20her%20eponymous%20first%20album%2C%20the%20well-reviewed%20%26quot%3BCassie%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20was%20released%20in%20the%20summer%20of%202006%20and%20included%20the%20popular%20single%20%26quot%3BMe%20%26amp%3B%20U.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAside%20from%20the%20sole%20album%2C%20Ventura%20released%20one%20mixtape%20and%20a%20handful%20of%20singles%20with%20Bad%20Boy%20Records%20over%20the%20years.%20She%20said%20she%20wasn't%20paid%20for%20the%20uncompleted%20nine%20albums%20that%20were%20part%20of%20the%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVentura%20said%20most%20of%20her%20time%20was%20spent%20preparing%20for%20and%20physically%20recuperating%20from%20%26quot%3Bfreak%20offs%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20she%20also%20called%20%26quot%3Bpartying.%26quot%3B%20She%20said%20the%20sex%20sessions%20led%20to%20dehydration%20and%20exhaustion%2C%20and%20that%20she%20took%20drugs%20to%20stay%20awake%20for%20several%20days%20in%20a%20row%20in%20order%20to%20have%20sex%20with%20other%20men%20at%20Combs'%20direction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20wasn't%20working%20on%20my%20music%2C%20I%20was%20recovering%20from%20partying%2C%26quot%3B%20Ventura%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat%20was%20a%20big%20chunk%20of%20my%20life.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225b668f7a-4da3-4627-b936-059c7daafbcb%5C%22%3EDiddy%20released%20just%20one%20Cassie%20album%20despite%20a%2010-album%20deal%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EVentura%20took%20the%20stand%20as%20the%20third%20witness%20to%20testify%20in%20Combs'%20sex-trafficking%20trial%20on%20Tuesday%20morning.%20Eight%20months%20pregnant%20with%20her%20third%20child%20with%20husband%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcassie-ventura-husband-alex-fine-video-sean-combs-assault-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAlex%20Fine%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20she%20wore%20a%20stretchy%20brown%20dress%20and%20camel%20overcoat%20in%20the%20lower%20Manhattan%20courtroom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20Ventura%20first%20signed%20onto%20Bad%20Boy%20Records%2C%20her%20relationship%20with%20Combs%20was%20platonic%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20things%20changed%20on%20her%2021st%20birthday%2C%20in%20August%202007%2C%20when%20they%20partied%20in%20Las%20Vegas%2C%20she%20said.%20There%2C%20Combs%20kissed%20Ventura%20in%20his%20hotel%20bathroom%2C%20she%20testified.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVentura%20wasn't%20sure%20what%20to%20do%2C%20she%20said.%20She%20was%20new%20to%20the%20music%20industry%20and%20couldn't%20grasp%20the%20power%20dynamics%20between%20herself%20and%20Combs%2C%20she%20testified.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20I%20was%20just%20confused%20at%20the%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20on%20the%20witness%20stand.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20a%20young%2C%20new%20artist%20who%20did%20not%20really%20know%20the%20lay%20of%20the%20land.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20her%20career%20was%20moving%20fast%2C%20and%20she%20said%20she%20recognized%20that%20Combs%2C%20as%20the%20head%20of%20her%20record%20label%2C%20controlled%20her%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20chose%20what%20was%20next%20for%20me%2C%20basically%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFine%2C%20Ventura's%20husband%2C%20appeared%20to%20hold%20back%20tears%20while%20Ventura%20testified.%20His%20face%20was%20ruddy%2C%20and%20he%20often%20appeared%20to%20swallow%20and%20rapidly