r%20Priyanka%2C%20the%20early%20days%20of%20motherhood%20felt%20less%20like%20an%20emotional%20whirlwind%20and%20more%20like%20checking%20things%20off%20a%20to-do%20list.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20turning%20point%20%E2%80%94%20that%20moment%20of%20surrender%20%E2%80%94%20that%20helped%20lighten%20her%20mental%20load.%20She%20began%20to%20focus%20on%20what%20truly%20needed%20her%20attention%3A%20her%20baby.%20And%20perhaps%2C%20slowly%2C%20herself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20so%20sleep%20deprived%20that%20all%20I%20just%20told%20myself%20was%20that%20I%20need%20to%20just%20keep%20the%20baby%20alive%20and%20healthy%2C%20everything%20else%20is%20secondary.%20As%20I%20found%20ways%20to%20ensure%20I%20got%20some%20good%20sleep%2C%20I%20gradually%20began%20to%20focus%20on%20the%20baby%20and%20only%20do%20that%2C%20while%20my%20husband%20took%20care%20of%20my%20recovery.%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20honesty%20is%20striking%20%E2%80%94%20something%20every%20new%20mom%20can%20likely%20relate%20to.%20The%20late-night%20Google%20searches%2C%20the%20endless%20advice%2C%20the%20contradictory%20dos%20and%20don%E2%80%99ts%20%E2%80%94%20all%20of%20it%20adds%20to%20the%20noise.%20And%20Priyanka%E2%80%99s%20been%20there%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EWhen%20in%20doubt%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20the%20first%20thing%20new%20mothers%20do%2C%20including%20me%2C%20is%20to%20browse.%20That%20itself%20gives%20a%20lot%20of%20stress.%20The%20research%20we%20do%20gives%20us%20a%20lot%20of%20information%2C%3Cem%3E%20which%20is%2C%20mostly%20contradicting%20what%20the%20doctor%20says.%20When%20we%20stop%20doing%20this%2C%20I%20think%20a%20lot%20of%20our%20mental%20load%20is%20off%20our%20heads%2C%20and%20new%20mothers%20can%20think%20clearly.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Priyanka%2C%20the%20early%20days%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebette